{"members":[{"header_text":" فس،  [تفسير  القمي ] : ","body_text":" <quranic_text>«حَتّٰي اِذٰا جٰاءَ اَحَدَهُمُ الْمَوْتُ»</quranic_text> <footnote>[المؤمنون۹۹]</footnote> اِلَي قَوْلِهِ: <quranic_text>«اِنَّهٰا كَلِمَةٌ هُوَ قٰائِلُهٰا»</quranic_text> <footnote>[المؤمنون۱۰۰]</footnote> فَاِنَّهَا نَزَلَتْ فِي مَانِعِ الزَّكَاةِ.","translation":"","aligned_body":"TAG_OPEN:quranic_text حَتّٰي اِذٰا جٰاءَ اَحَدَهُمُ الْمَوْتُ TAG_CLOSE:quranic_text TAG_OPEN:footnote المؤمنون ۹۹ TAG_CLOSE:footnote اِلَي قَوْلِهِ TAG_OPEN:quranic_text اِنَّهٰا كَلِمَةٌ هُوَ قٰائِلُهٰا TAG_CLOSE:quranic_text TAG_OPEN:footnote المؤمنون ۱۰۰ TAG_CLOSE:footnote فَاِنَّهَا نَزَلَتْ فِي مَانِعِ الزَّكَاةِ"}],"body_consensus_columns":[{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"word","token":"حتي","display":"حَتّٰي"},{"kind":"word","token":"اذا","display":"اِذٰا"},{"kind":"word","token":"جاء","display":"جٰاءَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"احدهم","display":"اَحَدَهُمُ"},{"kind":"word","token":"الموت","display":"الْمَوْتُ"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"footnote"},{"kind":"word","token":"المؤمنون","display":"المؤمنون"},{"kind":"word","token":"۹۹","display":"۹۹"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"footnote"},{"kind":"word","token":"الي","display":"اِلَي"},{"kind":"word","token":"قوله","display":"قَوْلِهِ"},{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"word","token":"انها","display":"اِنَّهٰا"},{"kind":"word","token":"كلمه","display":"كَلِمَةٌ"},{"kind":"word","token":"هو","display":"هُوَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"قائلها","display":"قٰائِلُهٰا"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"footnote"},{"kind":"word","token":"المؤمنون","display":"المؤمنون"},{"kind":"word","token":"۱۰۰","display":"۱۰۰"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"footnote"},{"kind":"word","token":"فانها","display":"فَاِنَّهَا"},{"kind":"word","token":"نزلت","display":"نَزَلَتْ"},{"kind":"word","token":"في","display":"فِي"},{"kind":"word